	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64483157"><p>Yes, neutron stars are also expected to have regions where there are no stable orbits. For anything less dense, the innermost stable orbit is below the surface.</p><p>The innermost stable orbit isn't related to the Roche limit or tides.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64483157">

